	<h1 class="title">埃博拉病毒也许有药可灭了，但谁能得到它？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/29515/small/29515.jgp?1420290761" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">ANDREW POLLACK</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2014-08-08 11:11:50 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/1785/medium/1785.jpg?1436645724" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="1785" data-title="《埃博拉病毒也许有药可灭了，但谁能得到它？》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/1785/medium/1785.jpg?1436645724" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/1785" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
